snippet.title: "CALL OF DOOM" Cinematic Launch Trailer // DOOM weapon MOD Project
snippet.description:
"Call of DOOM: Black Warfare" will be released in late January.

Call of DOOM: Black Warfare
https://www.moddb.com/mods/call-of-doom-cod-style-advanced-weapons-mod

This trailer is influenced by "Canceled DOOM 4 Prototype".
Focusing on the "human battle", I portrayed the battle between DOOM and DOOM 2 in a cinematic way.

USE MAPs:
-Don't play with Hell: Part 1
-E1M1 Remake: Doom 3 style
-Hell on Earth Starter pack
-HontE Remastered
-After DOOM
-Zones of Fear
-ITCM DOOM
-VOODOO GUNS
-Lost Civilization
-Planisphere 2
-Hell Core 2.0
-BlooM
